# Feature Documentation

After a **feature** is substantially complete, add one markdown file in `.agents/docs/features/`.

- Filename: kebab-case, e.g. `checkout-flow.md`

## Template

```markdown
# Feature title

## Summary
What was added or changed.

## Code areas
- Routes / pages: …
- Main components / files: …

## Verification
1. {{devCommand}}
2. Manual steps: …
```
